<% layout('/layouts/boilerplate') %>
    <h1 class="text-center sm-3">Our Story...</h1>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="row align-items-center mb-3">
            <div class="col"></div>
            <div class=" col-md-5 offset-1">
                <p class="d-flex story lh-lg">"I started smoking fish, turkey, beef sticks, and wild game back in 1975
                    with my old man. I remember my dad waking me up at the crack of dawn to get the smoker runnin’.
                    While I would have rather slept in back then, it taught me the importance of putting in the time
                    and care when smoking meats. Every time I fire up my own smoker I think of Dad and all that he
                    taught me, and not just about smoking. I have always loved cooking for large groups of people and
                    now, with our big orange trailer, I can share my cookin’ with even more people! It’s been a lot of
                    hard work but also a lot of fun. We hope you like it as much as we do." &nbsp;&nbsp;-Randy
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <div class="card offset-1" style="width: 24rem;">
                    <!-- <img src="/images/people/dad0.jpg" class="card-img-top img-fluid" alt="..."> -->
