                    <figure class="figure">
                        <img src="/images/people/lisa0.jpg" class="figure-img img-fluid rounded card-img-top" alt="...">
                        <figcaption class="figure-caption text-center">Lisa Johnson</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5" id="lisaStory">
                <p class="d-flex story lh-lg">"I was raised in the restaurant business. I have fond childhood memories
                    of
                    sitting on the prep table and
                    rolling meatballs and the excitement of pushing the big red button on the dishwasher. On busy days I
                    was very happy when my mom would put me in a corner with a cup, spoon and can of whipped cream.
                    Randy and I married in 2016. Randy proposed a BBQ food truck in 2021 as a fun job to do once he
                    “retired”. I was all in. I feel like I am following in my mom’s footsteps when fine tuning the mac
                    and
                    cheese and cornbread recipes. Preparing food is an expression of art and love. We hope you love our
                    food. Thank you for your patronage!" -Lisa</p>
